                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/753" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">HRM-0065</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">8721 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">M报社人员流失的困惑</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">The Confusion of Personnel Drain in M Newspaper Office</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">孔文，陈曦</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">东北财经大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大连M报社</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">新闻出版业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">人力资源管理部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">16 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">决策型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">报业；人力资源管理；记者流失</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Newspaper industry; Human resources management; Journalist turnover</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">      员工流失是员工流出的一种方式，是指员工从企业自愿流出，这种流出方式对于企业来讲是被动的，往往给企业带来特殊的损失。
    21世纪，报业竞争日趋白热化，传统的薪酬和绩效评价体系导致一线采编人员跳槽频繁，知识型员工的不断流失要求报业尽快实现人力资源科学化管理。中国记者网按单位类型对记者的统计数据显示，31-40岁的记者在报纸记者中所占比例最大，达到了32,597人，有调查显示这部分员工的流失风险也最大。
    本案例着重讨论了员工通过主动辞职和自动离职，与所在企业彻底解除法律契约关系这种显性员工流失现象。通过深入分析和探讨报业采编人员流失现状、原因及解决对策，寻求合理的报业知识型员工人力资源管理模式，为报业管理者提供决策参考。同时，在分析过程中，本案例也对报业这一特殊行业内部隐性记者流失现象及其原因和解决对策进行了初步探讨，以求对现代报业记者流失现象有一个全景式扫描，为人力资源管理教学提供更新的研究视角。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">    Staff turnover, a way of staff away, refers to voluntary outflow from the enterprise. This outflow is a passive way for the business enterprise and often brings the special damages to the business enterprise.
    In the 21st century, competition of newspaper industry has become increasingly fierce. The traditional payment and performance evaluation system lead to front-line editors changing jobs frequently. The constant loss of knowledge-based workers requires that newspaper industry realizes scientific management of human resources as soon as possible. According to various types of work units by Chinese Journalists, statistical data display that 31-40 year-old journalists up to 32,597 people take the largest proportion of newspaper journalists. A survey shows the risk about the loss of this part of the staff is greatest.
    This case focuses on dominant phenomenon of staff turnover, where staffs completely terminate the legal contract through active abdication and voluntary demission. This paper deeply analyses and discusses status, causes and solutions of newspaper editorial staff turnover in order to explore a reasonable human resources management mode of knowledge-based staff for managers to make a right direction. At the same time, in the analysis process, this case also makes a primary study on causes and solutions of recessive phenomenon of inner employee turnover in order to have a panoramic scanning on staff turnover of modern newspaper industry and offer a new viewpoint for teaching human resources management.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2011</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《人力资源管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">员工流失</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2012-02</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
